      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a good start. the 'ghetto' vibe works. can you expand on the people in the area though? like, if my main character is walking down a street and sees a group of locals hanging out on a corner, how would you describe them to make them look maybe a bit threatening or part of that 'social decay' you mentioned? just want to make sure the reader knows exactly what kind of crowd they're dealing with.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
